children.name: Rules
children.text:
Made from the tail of Limbbreaker the Beaverlisk, this paddle-like axe brings low any creature rooted in place.

This is a + 1 Greataxe that deals double damage to any creature or object made of wood. When you hit a creature you can use your reaction to force it to make a DC 14 strength saving throw or be knocked prone. This ability can be used a number of times per day equal to your proficiency bonus.
